{
  "3077850": {
    "name": "Trickster Trove",
    "steam_appid": 3077850,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/e12dc66fb2740190a28a1612afc00bc7.webp?t=1760313513\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“你们称之为地牢。而我看到的，是你们灵魂的倒影。你们用陷阱、怪物与自己恐惧的阴影筑成它。你们敞开大门，渴求他人的鲜血。其他人会为你们隐藏的宝物而来——他们会跳入火焰、毒液与尖刺，只为证明自己的力量。而你们，也会进入他们的地牢，明知每一步都可能是最后一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不是游戏，这是无尽的死亡交换。记住，在我的世界里没有胜者，只有死得稍晚的人。” —— 实体</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/fe60d9c3a15e44e4f09ffb2ed0484521.avif?t=1760313513\" width=617 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/4602f6f0040607d5f17775c8c0d78b2d.webp?t=1760313513\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/b2c1e606079420c01a3f9b9aff2f3859.avif?t=1760313513\" width=616 height=270 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地下城都由模块组成——房间与走廊相连，构成你自己的致命迷宫。其中有两个永远不变：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >入口——希望诞生之地。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/0dd711e49cfbe6c78cbe88defd8d4454.avif?t=1760313513\" width=616 height=335 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宝库——希望与一切同亡之处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/6e63ad6ea0c991030a2547f96a06baa6.avif?t=1760313513\" width=617 height=335 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它们之间的一切都属于你。岔路、死胡同、陷阱与怪物——这些都是你铸造堡垒的工具。迷宫中的每一步，都是你的意志。凡未能抵达宝库的灵魂，皆将它的奖赏留给你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/0e87829319b14d4df274b7ddcad3a6d3.webp?t=1760313513\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你决定踏上突袭时，请记住——那里没有地图，也没有提示。只有黑暗、危险，以及等待你失误的他人意志。每一个房间都会试图迷惑你。每一个陷阱都会考验你的专注。每一个怪物，都在等待你的到来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/ba84ff9fd9b09e5b5e508b88f4e29f22.avif?t=1760313513\" width=617 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >活下来——你将带走你所渴望的黄金。若死去——你的灵魂将任他人夺取。突袭不过是一场只有两种赌注的游戏：要么夺得他人的财富，要么失去自己的生命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/9a8acb8f30da0820065d11149cdade87.avif?t=1760313513\" width=617 height=347 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在突袭中的胜利，远不止是掠夺到的战利品。那是让你的地牢带来更多黄金、让你的灵魂变得更坚韧、更狡黠、更持久的一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/23e7f3854364ae6e74eed1996e376710.avif?t=1760313513\" width=616 height=334 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/682834ddac9efe9dd0cd443da0d3ea4c.webp?t=1760313513\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我收集了他们数个世纪——那些接受我条件、向黑暗挑战的最伟大的戏法者。他们的躯体如今安眠在我的收藏中。即便死亡，他们仍记得。每一个戏法者都有独特的能力、故事与一场可能与你更贴近的死亡——这一切无疑值得你关注。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/dc2c51c77e438eaed2c737fb5255b9f9.avif?t=1760313513\" width=616 height=331 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >若地下城击败了你，你将失去肉身、战利品与进度。只剩下渴求复仇的灵魂。从我的收藏中选取新的躯壳，继续这循环。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077850/extras/88c87f4080ae9b6d0baea10fed877f6e.avif?t=1760313513\" width=616 height=364 /></span></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 乌克兰语<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 波兰语, 日语, 简体中文<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
